---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Akash Mahajan"
  description="Founder of Kloudle and Appsecco. Building security tools, AI agents, and shipping in the open."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>
  <section class="about">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <p class="section-label reveal">About</p>

      <h1 class="about-title reveal reveal-d1">
        I'm Akash Mahajan.<br />
        I build security tools <span class="highlight">that people actually use.</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="about-body reveal reveal-d2">
        <p>
          I run two companies. <a href="https://kloudle.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kloudle</a> does
          cloud security — scanning, detection, and posture management built for teams shipping with
          AI agents. <a href="https://appsecco.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Appsecco</a> does
          application security consulting and training, from traditional pentesting to AI red teaming.
        </p>

        <p>
          Beyond the companies, I build and maintain over a dozen open-source projects. Security scanners,
          Claude Code plugins, educational tools, community resources. I believe the best way to improve
          security is to make the tools accessible and the knowledge open.
        </p>

        <p>
          I ship fast, I ship in the open, and I write about what I learn along the way.
          This site is where all of that comes together.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-links reveal reveal-d3">
        <a href="https://x.com/makash" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-link">
          <span class="link-label">X / Twitter</span>
          <span class="link-handle">@makash</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/makash" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-link">
          <span class="link-label">GitHub</span>
          <span class="link-handle">makash</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/akashm/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-link">
          <span class="link-label">LinkedIn</span>
          <span class="link-handle">/in/akashm</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@makash" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-link">
          <span class="link-label">YouTube</span>
          <span class="link-handle">@makash</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 10rem var(--gutter) 4rem;
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 42rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .about-body {
    max-width: 38rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-body a {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-border-light);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: text-decoration-color 0.2s;
  }
  .about-body a:hover { text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent); color: var(--color-accent); }

  .about-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 38rem;
  }

  .about-link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: var(--color-text);
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .about-link:hover { background: var(--color-surface-hover); color: var(--color-text); }

  .link-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono), monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .link-handle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about { padding: 7rem var(--gutter) 3rem; }
    .about-links { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
